WEBVTT

00:00.984 --> 00:02.410
My name is Elena Gilbert.

00:02.411 --> 00:04.213
I'm a vampire
in search of the cure.

00:04.214 --> 00:05.626
It's a cure
for immortality?

00:05.627 --> 00:08.169
You dig up Silas,
and you've got your cure.

00:08.170 --> 00:09.784
There is only
one dose.

00:09.785 --> 00:11.833
I really want to get
that cure for you.

00:11.834 --> 00:13.744
If I gave you the cure
to save yourself,

00:13.745 --> 00:15.724
you'd give it to Elena,
wouldn't you?

00:15.725 --> 00:18.220
We all wanted to help
Elena get the damn thing...

00:18.221 --> 00:20.107
We risked everything
to get it.

00:21.167 --> 00:23.465
- She's here.
- Aagh!

00:23.466 --> 00:25.580
It's been too long,
little Gilbert.

00:31.949 --> 00:33.620
And we failed.

