01:00.048 --> 01:03.217
Jeremy!
Oh, no. No. No.

01:03.218 --> 01:06.787
Oh, no.
Oh, God, no.

01:06.788 --> 01:09.823
Oh, God...

01:09.824 --> 01:11.558
It's fine.
It's fine. It's fine.

01:11.559 --> 01:13.093
You're gonna be ok.

01:13.094 --> 01:14.628
The ring will
bring you back.

01:14.629 --> 01:18.298
It's ok. It's ok.
You're gonna be ok.

01:18.299 --> 01:19.900
You're gonna
be ok, Jeremy.

01:19.901 --> 01:21.368
You're gonna be fine.

01:23.004 --> 01:24.271
How'd this happen?

01:24.272 --> 01:25.706
It was Katherine.

01:25.707 --> 01:26.740
She must have been
following us this whole time.

01:26.741 --> 01:28.509
What about the cure
or Silas?

01:28.510 --> 01:31.145
If there was anything
in there at all, it's all gone.

01:31.146 --> 01:32.379
Where the hell
is Bonnie?

01:32.380 --> 01:33.427
I have no idea.

01:33.428 --> 01:34.581
She went looking
for Jeremy last night.

01:34.582 --> 01:36.517
She never came back.

01:36.518 --> 01:39.353
Damon, Elena is in there
waiting for the Gilbert ring

01:39.354 --> 01:40.988
to bring Jeremy
back to life.

01:40.989 --> 01:42.689
Ok. Fine.
We'll wait with her.

01:42.690 --> 01:45.150
Damon, listen to me.

01:45.927 --> 01:48.762
Jeremy was
one of the five,

01:48.763 --> 01:51.064
a hunter.

01:53.625 --> 01:56.153
He's supernatural.

01:56.967 --> 01:58.905
The ring
won't work anymore.

02:02.641 --> 02:04.977
She won't
survive this.

02:06.613 --> 02:08.082
I'll find Bonnie.

02:08.083 --> 02:09.681
You get Elena
off this island.

02:16.460 --> 02:21.012
